y problems  notify the Director of International Programs and provide written documentation of the allegations Academic Programs International Programs Home Study Abroad Online Application Study Abroad International Cadets Financial Assistance Passports and Visas Faculty Led Programs Independent International Travel Parents International Programs Staff Patricia Hardin Assistant Director P   540  464 7421 F   540  464 7768 E  International Programs Virginia Military Institute Old Hospital Lexington  VA  24450  Academic Programs International Programs Home Study Abroad Online Application Study Abroad International Cadets Financial Assistance Passports and Visas Faculty Led Programs Independent International Travel Parents International Programs Staff Patricia Hardin Assistant Director P   540  464 7421 F   540  464 7768 E  International Programs Virginia Military Institute Old Hospital Lexington  VA  24450 Academic Programs International Programs Home Study Abroad Online Application Study Abroad International Cadets Financial Assistance Passports and Visas Faculty Led Programs Independent International Travel Parents International Programs Staff Academic Programs Academic Programs International Programs Home International Programs Home Study Abroad Online Application Study Abroad Online Application Study Abroad Study Abroad International Cadets International Cadets Financial Assistance Financial Assistance Passports and Visas Passports and Visas Faculty Led Programs Faculty Led Programs Independent International Travel Independent International Travel Parents Parents International Programs Staff International Programs Staff Patricia Hardin Assistant Director P   540  464 7421 F   540  464 7768 E  International Programs Virginia Military Institute Old Hospital Lexington  VA  24450 Patricia Hardin Assistant Director P   540  464 7421 F   540  464 7768 E  International Programs Virginia Military Institute Old Hospital Lexington  VA  24450 Patricia Hardin      Internation